title: [Icemule, Brewer's Alley]
description: The impressive west wall dominates the view of this alley, towering over the various squat buildings and the randomly placed kiosks.  Bright pennants of different colors snap in the wind from dark doorways, attempting to draw the eyes of the occasional person who wanders past.

The impressive west wall dominates the view of this alley, casting a long shadow over the various squat buildings and the randomly placed kiosks.  Pennants of muted colors snap in the wind from lit doorways, attempting to draw the eyes of the occasional person who wanders past.
